snippet.title: Rise of Agon - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
LAUNCHING MAY 5th - https://www.riseofagon.com/
Rise of Agon is an open world sandbox MMO with player controlled empire building and politics, action based first person PVP combat with full loot, and naval warfare on the open seas. 

Battle with thousands of players with weapons and armor crafted by our players. Work together to build cities, siege engines and over 25 naval ships.

Rise of Agon gives you the freedom to explore new lands, conquer enemies and forge alliances where risk vs reward dictate the choices you make.

Music composed by Gregory Bakay: http://gregory-bakay.wixsite.com/music

Rise of Agon trailer
